Cell["\<\
A single random number taken drawn from the Bernoulli distribution with \
probability of success equal to 0.3:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781622508019147*^9, 3.7816225339206953`*^9}, {
  3.948083395710354*^9, 3.948083407336688*^9}, {3.94808397318495*^9, 
